stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Unauthenticated: Start app

    Unauthenticated --> LoggingIn: submit credentials
    LoggingIn --> Authenticated: signInWithPassword success
    LoggingIn --> Unauthenticated: invalid credentials / network error

    Authenticated --> Unauthenticated: signOut / token expired / network failure
    Authenticated --> Unauthenticated: user deactivated (is_active = false)

    state Authenticated {
        [*] --> NormalUser
        NormalUser --> AdminUser: is_admin = true && is_active
        AdminUser --> NormalUser: admin toggled off
    }

    Unauthenticated --> Registering: open register page
    Registering --> AwaitingEmailConfirmation: signUp without auto session
    Registering --> Unauthenticated: auto-confirmed + redirected to login
    Registering --> Unauthenticated: duplicate username/email

    AwaitingEmailConfirmation --> ResendingVerification: resend link
    AwaitingEmailConfirmation --> Authenticated: email verified via link + setSession + signOut back to login

    Authenticated --> ResettingPassword: forgot password -> email -> recovery link
    ResettingPassword --> Authenticated: new password set successfully
    ResettingPassword --> Unauthenticated: invalid/expired recovery token

    note right of Authenticated
        Session managed by Supabase:
        - access_token
        - refresh_token
        - autoRefreshToken
    end note

    note right of AwaitingEmailConfirmation
        User stored in localStorage
        as svu_pending_verification_email
    end note
